{
  "texts": [
    "These libraries will form a great basis towards the development of hyperbolic learning.",
    "• Large and multimodal learning In computer vision, and Artificial Intelligence in general, there is a strong trend towards learning at large scale and learning with multiple modalities, e.g., image-text or video-audio models.",
    "It is therefore a natural desire for the field to arrive at hyperbolic foundation models.",
    "While early work has shown that large-scale and/or multimodal learning is viable with hyperbolic embeddings (Desai et al., 2023), hyperbolic foundation models form a longer-term commitment as they require solutions to all open problems mentioned above, from stable, fully hyperbolic learning to continued open source development.",
    "• Multiple hyperbolic models Unique to hyperbolic geometry is the existence of multiple models to perform numerical operations."
  ]
}